
================
Development sets
================
The AP17-OLR Challenge provides 3 development sets of the 10 languages in data/:
dev_all, the original development set, 17964 utterances in total.
dev_1s, each utterance of dev_all is segmented to 1 second, all utterances remain. 
dev_3s, each utterance of dev_all is segmented to 3 seconds, 16404 utterances remain, others don't reach 3 seconds and are omitted.



